Usage: deletePinFromPinGroup [-help] [-cell <string>] -pin {pinNameList}
                             -pinGroup <string>

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>         # Specifies name of the module. (string, optional)
-pin {pinNameList}     # Specifies the name(s) of the port(s) of the module.
                       # (string, required)
-pinGroup <string>     # Specifies the name of the pin group that was created.
                       # (string, required)